blog.description: a quarterly, printed magazine about contemporary collage.

summary:
Kolaj Magazine is the world’s only internationally-oriented art magazine dedicated to contemporary collage.

  If you don’t know...
caption:
Kolaj Magazine is the world’s only internationally-oriented art magazine dedicated to contemporary collage.

If you don’t know collage,
you don’t know contemporary art.

CURRENT ISSUE

KOLAJ #22

Kolaj #22 delivers a look at the wonderful world of contemporary collage: the people who make it and the people who love it. Belgian artist Strook‘s building-sized collage is on the cover of the issue. In her profile of the artist, Etty Yaniv writes, “The found wood pieces Strook fuses in his assemblages and the imagery he depicts in his collaged paintings manifest an act of revival: allocating fragmented elements of decay by making an artistic use for them and out of them.” MORE

Kolaj is a full colour, internationally-oriented art magazine. Get your copy today!

summary: Art Commissions OpenedThis is an information post of my art commission for tuition supply. To order me a pic, please send...
caption:
Art Commissions Opened

This is an information post of my art commission for tuition supply. To order me a pic, please send private message to this account. Ppl having difficulty with describing character or making specific requirements for commission can use/refer this form.(Downloadable link of form made in .xlsx file)

Info

• There are no slots system for now. I would do multiple works as possible and maybe make the number of slots later.
• I sketch/ink on paper and edit/colour with Medibang mobile.
• Basic price is for the coloured version.
• Acceptable payments are USD by PayPal/KRW remittance/DeviantArt points.(Notify me about this and I will tell the cost following to exchange rate.)
• Complete file’s Google drive link or email will be sent after the payment.
• I don’t afford refund or redrawing after the rough sketch is completed.

Types & Prices

• Basic style: $12 for headshot / $18 for halfbody / $24 for fullbody
• Chibi: $12 for fullbody
• Ref sheet(Customs available): $28 for coloured / $10 for b&w
• Comic(per one page): $30 for coloured / $24 for b&w
• Very complex design or background may have fee depending on its complexity.
• Minus $6 from total price for b&w.
• Ordering multiple works makes discounts.
• For DeviantArt points, multiply 100 from USD.

For more samples, take a view of my pictures tagged posts.

++Here is also Ko-fi commission for simple sketches(headshot/chibi only) for $3! Have a look :D

summary: Emergency Commissions OPEN!
body:
Emergency Commissions OPEN!

Sooo… after a few months with various unplanned expenses, things got topped off with me having a car accident yesterday.

I’m fine, I was lucky no one got injured. But I very nearly totalled the car. It’s not an expensive car, but it has a huge sentimental value so I obviously want to get it fixed asap. But this is just the one invoice I won’t be able to afford out of my pocket.

So, I’m opening commissions.

I will draw birthday cards (link to seperate post here) for 15$ per piece (plus shipping)

I will do little drawings for you - A6 for 5$, A5 for 10$ (plus shipping)

I am happy to write small fanfiction - under 1000 words for 5$, above 1000 words for 10$

(Here’s my AO3 account!)


All payments via paypal!

Message me!


(Please reblog ;;________;;)
